%% Diagram: Optimistic Update Reconciliation
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant CA as Client A
    participant MP as Server (Rust)
    participant CB as Client B

    Note over CA: A edits O.fill = red
    CA->>CA: apply locally,<br/>mark unacked
    CA->>MP: delta(O.fill=red, seq 42)

    Note over CB: B edits O.fill = blue
    CB->>CB: apply locally,<br/>mark unacked
    CB->>MP: delta(O.fill=blue, seq 43)

    Note over MP: Apply in arrival order<br/>seq 43 wins
    MP-->>CA: broadcast(blue, seq 43)
    MP-->>CB: ack(blue, seq 43)

    Note over CA: Discard server P while<br/>local P is unacked
    CA->>CA: keep red

    MP-->>CA: ack(red, seq 42)
    Note over MP: Re-broadcast wins/loss order
    MP-->>CB: broadcast(red, seq 42)

    CA->>CA: clear unacked, finalize red
    CB->>CB: replace local, finalize red
